BaseParam0.Description: Affects physical damage dealt by gladiator's arms, marauder's arms, dark knight's arms, gunbreaker's arms, pugilist's arms, lancer's arms, samurai's arms, reaper's arms, thaumaturge's arms, arcanist's arms, red mage's arms, pictomancer's arms, conjurer's arms, astrologian's arms, sage's arms, and blue mage's arms.
BaseParam0.Description_de: Stärke: Beeinflusst die Höhe des physischen Schadens, den die Waffen der Gladiatoren, Marodeure, Revolverklingen, Faustkämpfer, Pikeniere, Druiden, Thaumaturgen, Hermetiker, Dunkelritter, Samurai, Rotmagier, Piktomaten, Blaumagier, Astrologen, Schnitter und Weisen austeilen.
BaseParam0.Description_en: Affects physical damage dealt by gladiator's arms, marauder's arms, dark knight's arms, gunbreaker's arms, pugilist's arms, lancer's arms, samurai's arms, reaper's arms, thaumaturge's arms, arcanist's arms, red mage's arms, pictomancer's arms, conjurer's arms, astrologian's arms, sage's arms, and blue mage's arms.
BaseParam0.Description_fr: Influence les dégâts physiques des épées, épées à deux mains, haches, armes de corps à corps, armes d'hast, katana, armes de faucheur, rapières, pistolames, bâtons, baguettes, pinceaux, grimoires, globes célestes, armes de sage et armes de mage bleu.
BaseParam0.Description_ja: 片手剣・両手斧・両手剣・ガンブレード・格闘武器・両手槍・刀・両手鎌・呪具・魔道書・細剣・筆・幻具・天球儀・賢具・青魔器による物理攻撃力に影響を与えます。
BaseParam0.Name: Strength

BaseParam1.Description: Affects physical damage dealt by rogue's arms, viper's arms, archer's arms, machinist's arms, and dancer's arms.
BaseParam1.Description_de: Geschick: Beeinflusst die Höhe des physischen Schadens, den die Waffen von Waldläufern, Vipern, Schurken, Maschinisten und Tänzern austeilen.
BaseParam1.Description_en: Affects physical damage dealt by rogue's arms, viper's arms, archer's arms, machinist's arms, and dancer's arms.
BaseParam1.Description_fr: Influence les dégâts physiques des dagues, lames jumelles, arcs et armes à feu et de jet.
BaseParam1.Description_ja: 双剣・二刀流武器・弓・銃・投擲武器による物理攻撃力に影響を与えます。
BaseParam1.Name: Dexterity

BaseParam2.Description_de: Konstitution: Beeinflusst die Höhe der maximalen Lebenspunkte (LP).
BaseParam2.Description_ja: 最大HPに影響を与えます。
BaseParam2.Name: Vitality

BaseParam3.Description: Affects the rate at which your physical and magic attacks land direct hits, dealing slightly more damage than normal hits. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be direct. Higher values will also result in greater damage for actions which guarantee direct hits.
BaseParam3.Description_de: Direkter Treffer: Je höher dieser Wert, desto wahrscheinlicher ist es, dass deine physischen oder magischen Attacken einen direkten Treffer landen und mehr Schaden anrichten. Bei Kommandos mit automatischen direkten Treffern wird der Schaden erhöht.
BaseParam3.Description_en: Affects the rate at which your physical and magic attacks land direct hits, dealing slightly more damage than normal hits. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be direct. Higher values will also result in greater damage for actions which guarantee direct hits.
BaseParam3.Description_fr: Accroît les chances que les dégâts infligés par les attaques physiques et magiques soient augmentés. Une valeur élevée accroît la fréquence des coups nets. Si une action en inflige nécessairement un, les chances de coups nets augmentent les dégâts infligés.
BaseParam3.Description_ja:
物理・魔法攻撃により与えるダメージ量が一定割合増加します。

ダイレクトヒットが高いほど、ダイレクトヒットが発生しやすくなります。

ダイレクトヒットの発生が確定となるアクションを実行する場合は、与えるダメージ量に影響を与えます。

その際にはダイレクトヒットが高いほどダメージ量が増加します。
BaseParam3.Name: Direct Hit Rate

BaseParamSpecial0.Description: Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_de: Verteidigung: Je höher dieser Wert, desto weniger physischen Schaden erleidest du.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_en: Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_fr: Influence le montant de dégâts reçus lorsqu'une attaque physique est subie. Une défense élevée permet de subir moins de dégâts.
BaseParamSpecial0.Description_ja:
物理攻撃を受けた際のダメージを軽減します。

物理防御力が高いほど、物理攻撃によって受けるダメージが小さくなります。
BaseParamSpecial0.Name: Defense

BaseParamSpecial1.Description: Affects the amount of damage taken by magic attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial1.Description_de: Magieabwehr: Je höher dieser Wert, desto weniger Magieschaden erleidest du.
BaseParamSpecial1.Description_en: Affects the amount of damage taken by magic attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.
BaseParamSpecial1.Description_fr: Influence le montant de dégâts reçus lorsqu'une attaque magique est subie. Une défense magique élevée permet de subir moins de dégâts.
BaseParamSpecial1.Description_ja:
攻撃魔法を受けた際のダメージを軽減します。

魔法防御力が高いほど、魔法攻撃によって受けるダメージが小さくなります。
BaseParamSpecial1.Name: Magic Defense

ItemSoulCrystal.Description: Upon the back of this crystal plaque are engraved the myriad creations of leatherworkers from eras past.
ItemSoulCrystal.Description_de: Wenn du diesen Handwerker-Kristall anlegst, wirst du als Gerber zum Spezialisten.
ItemSoulCrystal.Description_en: Upon the back of this crystal plaque are engraved the myriad creations of leatherworkers from eras past.
ItemSoulCrystal.Description_fr: Ce joyau renferme les souvenirs et les secrets des tanneurs des temps passés.
ItemSoulCrystal.Description_ja: 革細工師のマイスターとして認められた証
ItemSoulCrystal.Name: Soul of the Leatherworker
ItemSoulCrystal.Name_ja: マイスターの証:革細工師
ItemSoulCrystal.Singular_ja: マイスターの証:革細工師

ItemGlamour.Description:
This crystalline prism captures the likeness of a piece of equipment and projects it onto another object of comparable form and function.



[Necessary to project glamours.]
ItemGlamour.Description_de:
Ein kleiner Kristall, der magische Lichtstrahlen flicht und Ausrüstungsgegenständen eine andere Erscheinung geben kann.

Erforderlich für Projektionen.
ItemGlamour.Description_en:
This crystalline prism captures the likeness of a piece of equipment and projects it onto another object of comparable form and function.



[Necessary to project glamours.]
ItemGlamour.Description_fr:
Ce bloc de cristal taillé projette de la lumière, permettant de créer une illusion.

[Permet de créer une illusion pour un équipement]
ItemGlamour.Description_ja:
魔法の光で記憶させた武具の幻影を映し出す小結晶

[武具投影に必要]
ItemGlamour.Name: Glamour Prism

Item.Description:
It has recently been discovered that this substance of unknown origin has the faculty to assimilate with other forms of matter, effectively restoring them to their original condition. This specific grade of dark matter has been shown to bond best with items crafted from standard materials.



[Used to repair equipment for levels 1-30.]
Item.Description_de: Diese mysteriöse Substanz kann Materie assimilieren und sämtliche Eigenschaften der kopierten Materie übernehmen, was sie zu einem perfekten Material für Reparaturen von Ausrüstungsgegenständen der Stufen 1 bis 30 macht.
Item.Description_en:
It has recently been discovered that this substance of unknown origin has the faculty to assimilate with other forms of matter, effectively restoring them to their original condition. This specific grade of dark matter has been shown to bond best with items crafted from standard materials.



[Used to repair equipment for levels 1-30.]
Item.Description_fr: Un minerai réagissant à l'énergie spirituelle, et qui a des facultés d'assimilation avec d'autres matières. Convient aux équipements de niveau 1 à 30.
Item.Description_ja:
他物質への同化特性を持つ精神感応型物質。グレード3

[レベル1～30の装備向け汎用修理材料]
Item.Name: Grade 3 Dark Matter
Item.Plural_fr: fragments de matière sombre grade III
Item.Singular_fr: fragment de matière sombre grade III
